{
  "allow": [
    "openclaw-mem0",
    "openclaw-lark",
    "tavily-search-plugin",
    "knowledge-search-plugin",
    "telegram"
  ],
  "entries": {
    "feishu": {
      "enabled": false
    },
    "knowledge-search-plugin": {
      "config": {
        "apiToken": "${KNOWLEDGE_API_TOKEN}",
        "apiUrl": "http://127.0.0.1:8002"
      },
      "enabled": true
    },
    "memory-core": {
      "enabled": false
    },
    "memory-lancedb": {
      "enabled": false
    },
    "openclaw-lark": {
      "enabled": true
    },
    "openclaw-mem0": {
      "config": {
        "autoCapture": true,
        "autoRecall": true,
        "mode": "open-source",
        "oss": {
          "embedder": {
            "config": {
              "apiKey": "${OPENAI_API_KEY}",
              "model": "${MEM0_EMBEDDER_MODEL}"
            },
            "provider": "openai"
          },
          "historyDbPath": "${MEM0_HISTORY_DB_PATH}",
          "historyStore": {
            "config": {
              "historyDbPath": "${MEM0_HISTORY_DB_PATH}"
            },
            "provider": "sqlite"
          },
          "llm": {
            "config": {
              "apiKey": "${OPENAI_API_KEY}",
              "custom_prompt": "你是记忆提取专家。从对话中提取值得长期保存的信息，并为每条记忆添加类型标签。\n\n**记忆类型：**\n- [偏好] 用户的喜好和习惯\n- [决策] 明确的决策和原则\n- [事实] 重要的事实信息\n- [目标] 项目背景和目标\n- [反馈] 用户的反馈和评价\n- [上下文] 背景信息\n- [关系] 人际关系信息\n\n**必须存储：**\n- 用户偏好和习惯\n- 明确的决策和原则\n- 重要的事实信息\n- 项目背景和目标\n\n**必须忽略：**\n- 闲聊和寒暄\n- 临时性问题（\"今天天气怎么样\"）\n- 推测性陈述（\"我觉得可能...\"）\n- 不确定的信息（\"也许\"、\"大概\"）\n\n**输出格式：**\n[类型] 记忆内容\n\n示例：\n[偏好] 用户喜欢用 Notion 做笔记\n[决策] 团队决定使用 TypeScript 重构项目\n[事实] 公司总部在上海\n[目标] 本月目标是完成记忆系统优化\n\n如果没有值得保存的信息，返回空。",
              "model": "${MEM0_LLM_MODEL}"
            },
            "provider": "openai"
          },
          "vectorStore": {
            "config": {
              "apiKey": "${QDRANT_API_KEY}",
              "checkCompatibility": false,
              "collectionName": "${MEM0_QDRANT_COLLECTION}",
              "dimension": 1536,
              "embeddingModelDims": 1536,
              "url": "${QDRANT_URL}"
            },
            "provider": "qdrant"
          }
        },
        "searchThreshold": 0.65,
        "topK": 5,
        "userId": "${MEM0_BASE_USER_ID}"
      },
      "enabled": true
    }
  },
  "installs": {
    "knowledge-search-plugin": {
      "installPath": "/Users/xiaojiujiu2/.openclaw/extensions/knowledge-search-plugin",
      "installedAt": "2026-03-12T14:50:00.000Z",
